 tracking-wide underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"#size-guide\">Size guide</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\" role=\"radiogroup\" aria-label=\"Select size\" aria-required=\"true\"><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XS\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XS\" name=\"size\" value=\"xs\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XS</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"S\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"S\" name=\"size\" value=\"s\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">S</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"M\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"M\" name=\"size\" value=\"m\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">M</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"L\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"L\" name=\"size\" value=\"l\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">L</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XL\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XL\" name=\"size\" value=\"xl\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XL</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XXL\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XXL\" name=\"size\" value=\"xxl\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XXL</span></label></div></fieldset><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted mt-3 leading-relaxed\">Cropped oversized fit. Size up for more coverage, size down for the intended proportion.</p><a class=\"inline-block text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors mt-2\" href=\"/support/size-guide\">Size guide →</a></div><div class=\"rule\"></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-kvrn-text text-kvrn-bg border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-[#333333] hover:border-[#333333] active:bg-black active:border-black disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-[56px] px-9 text-[13px] w-full\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Select a Size</span></button></div><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\" aria-label=\"Order information\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6l2.5 2.5L10 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Secure checkout</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6l2.5 2.5L10 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Store credit returns within return window</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6l2.5 2.5L10 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Ships within 1–3 business days</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted\"><svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6l2.5 2.5L10 3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Premium materials, tested per batch</li></ul><div class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border border-t border-kvrn-border\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-construction\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">The Construction<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-construction\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-construction\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-0.5\">500 GSM French Terry Blend</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">70% cotton, 30% polyester. Heavier than the standard collection. Dense with a slightly textured face.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-0.5\">Enzyme Washed</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Each piece is enzyme washed before shipping for an immediate softness. No break-in period.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-0.5\">Pre-Shrunk</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Pre-shrunk to lock in the fit. Wrinkle-resistant finish maintains the silhouette through regular wear.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-0.5\">Cropped Proportion</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Sits at the hip rather than the thigh. The intended silhouette for the Phantom collection.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-specs\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Specifications<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-specs\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-specs\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><dl class=\"space-y-2\"><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Material</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">70% Cotton, 30% Polyester</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Weight</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">500 GSM</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Construction</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">French terry blend</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Finish</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Enzyme washed, wrinkle-resistant</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Pre-shrunk</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Yes</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Fit</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Oversized, cropped</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-4\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text min-w-[110px]\">Care</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\">Machine wash cold. Tumble dry low.</dd></div></dl></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-shipping\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Shipping<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-shipping\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-shipping\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\"><p>Orders are processed within approximately 1–3 business days.</p><p>Domestic delivery: 2–7 business days.</p><p>International delivery: 5–14+ business days.</p><p>Delivery estimates are not guarantees. Actual costs calculated at checkout based on destination and method.</p><a class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\" href=\"/support/shipping-returns\">Full shipping policy →</a></div></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-returns\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Returns<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-returns\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-returns\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted\"><p>We accept returns for store credit within our return window on unworn, unwashed items with tags attached.</p><p>Customer is responsible for return shipping costs unless the item is faulty, damaged, or incorrect.</p><a class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\" href=\"/support/shipping-returns#returns\">Full returns policy →</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"mt-20 md:mt-28\" aria-labelledby=\"construction-section\"><p id=\"construction-section\" class=\"label-11 mb-8 text-center\">The Construction</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-5 space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase\">500 GSM French Terry Blend</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">70% cotton, 30% polyester. Heavier than the standard collection. Dense with a slightly textured face.</p></div><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-5 space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase\">Enzyme Washed</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Each piece is enzyme washed before shipping for an immediate softness. No break-in period.</p></div><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-5 space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase\">Pre-Shrunk</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Pre-shrunk to lock in the fit. Wrinkle-resistant finish maintains the silhouette through regular wear.</p></div><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-5 space-y-2\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest uppercase\">Cropped Proportion</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Sits at the hip rather than the thigh. The intended silhouette for the Phantom collection.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"mt-20 md:mt-28\" aria-labelledby=\"set-section\"><div class=\"border-t border-kvrn-border pt-12\"><p id=\"set-section\" class=\"label-11 mb-8\">Complete the Set</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 items-start\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><a class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] bg-kvrn-bg-raised overflow-hidden block\" href=\"/products/kvrn-phantom-hoodie\"><img alt=\"KVRN Phantom Hoodie in black, front view\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"200px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fphantom-hoodie-black-front.webp&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fphantom-hoodie-black-front.webp&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2